From 4ad397bbdd3c24874518b00b1cfe82b2f2b16d18 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Azat Mukhametshin <azatm@microsoft.com>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 13:16:18 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 02/32] Add Microsoft.Testing.Extensions.GitHubActionsReport
 with per-assembly log groups

Implements the first requirement of #9142: a new GitHub Actions report extension that emits ::group:: / ::endgroup:: workflow commands per test assembly so the runner UI collapses each assembly's output. Auto-activates when GITHUB_ACTIONS=true; controllable via --report-gh-groups on/off and --report-gh.

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>
